submenu\nABOUT US\nOUR TEAM\nOUR COMMUNITY IMPACT\nHOME\nCAREERS\nAcuitas is a GREAT place to work.\nTESTIMONIALS\n\n“I’ve worked at more than 10 different companies during my career, and nothing comes close to my experience at Acuitas. The respect I’ve been shown and the empowerment I’ve been given have been second to none. I have the freedom and flexibility to perform my tasks according to my own schedule and preferences. I truly felt like a valued team member from day one.”\n\n– Will, Senior Manager, Finance\n\n“Acuitas offers a unique work environment culture that sets it apart. The atmosphere is both collaborative and innovative, fostering creativity and growth. I have opportunities to work on diverse, exciting projects with an incredibly talented and supportive team that values collaboration and creativity. The company’s commitment to employee development and well-being is truly exceptional. Something that stands out is how relaxed, but efficient the team is. I’m grateful to be part of such a forward-thinking and dynamic", "crawl_error": "", "stage2_checked_at_utc": "2026-07-18T14:48:15.231549+00:00", "stage2_result": "confirmed_career_landing_unresolved", "stage2_reason": "Valid career landing page; downstream job source not resolved", "resolved_monitor_url": "https://acuitastx.com/careers/", "resolved_ats": "", "stage2_jsonld_jobposting_count": "0", "stage2_probable_job_link_count": "0", "stage2_sample_job_links": "", "candidate_urls_found": "", "candidate_visits_json": "[]", "stage2_error": "", "stage2b_checked_at_utc": "2026-07-19T00:53:07.304668+00:00", "stage2b_result": "career_page_still_unresolved", "stage2b_reason": "Career page confirmed, but no downstream listing or job API was found", "stage2b_monitor_url": "https://acuitastx.com/careers/", "stage2b_provider": "", "stage2b_job_api_url": "", "stage2b_network_candidate_count": 1, "stage2b_network_candidates_json": "[{\"url\": \"https://acuitastx.com/careers/\", \"status\": 200, \"resource_type\": \"d