ents & Graduates\nAlstom University\nCandidate data privacy\nJoin Alstom\nThe Alstom Experience\nYour career at Alstom\nStudents & Graduates\nShare\nJoin Alstom\n\nWe look for curious and innovative people who are passionate about working together to reinvent mobility, making it smarter and more sustainable. Visit our career portal to search our job openings or to create an account in our candidate database.\n\nBrowse jobs\n\nThe Alstom Experience\n\nAt Alstom, we value curious and innovative people who are passionate about working together to reinvent mobility, making it smarter and more sustainable.\n\nJoin the Alstom Experience\n\nCaring by nature\nJoin a community that cares about people... and therefore, cares for people\n\nWe are committed to accompanying our people throughout their career at Alstom. We strive to provide all our employees with learning, mobility and career opportunities as well as the empowerment they need to succeed in their professional lives. Dialogue, cooperation and teamwork are at the heart of our commun", "crawl_error": "", "stage2_checked_at_utc": "2026-07-18T14:51:28.786830+00:00", "stage2_result": "confirmed_career_landing_unresolved", "stage2_reason": "Valid career landing page; downstream job source not resolved", "resolved_monitor_url": "https://www.alstom.com/careers", "resolved_ats": "", "stage2_jsonld_jobposting_count": "0", "stage2_probable_job_link_count": "0", "stage2_sample_job_links": "", "candidate_urls_found": "70:https://jobsearch.alstom.com/ | 60:https://www.alstom.com/careers#main-content | 60:https://www.alstom.com/careers/alstom-experience", "candidate_visits_json": "[{\"url\": \"https://jobsearch.alstom.com/\", \"result\": \"confirmed_career_landing_unresolved\", \"ats\": \"\", \"score\": 70}, {\"url\": \"https://www.alstom.com/careers/alstom-experience\", \"result\": \"confirmed_career_landing_unresolved\", \"ats\": \"\", \"score\": 60}]", "stage2_error": "", "stage2b_checked_at_utc": "2026-07-19T01:00:26.492421+0